    </section>

    <section class="cards-section">
      <h2>Caring Beyond Measure</h2>
      <p>Discover our mission to nurture and provide love to each child.</p>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/images/img2.jpg" alt="Family Connections">
          <h3>Family Connections</h3>
          <p>Strengthen relationships by facilitating heartfelt connections and communication.</p>
          <button>Learn more</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/images/img3.jpg" alt="Caring Classrooms">
          <h3>Caring Classrooms</h3>
          <p>Cultivate compassionate learning spaces with engaging and supportive interactions.</p>
          <button>Learn more</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/images/img4.jpg.jpg" alt="Family Bonds">
          <h3>Family Bonds</h3>
          <p>Nurture bonds within the community through shared experiences and activities.</p>
          <button>Learn more</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="community-section">
      <h2>Our Community's Voices</h2>
      <blockquote>
        <p>"Adopting through Sunshine Orphanage was a life-changing experience for our family. The love and care every child receives from this compassionate staff is heartwarming. Seeing smiles on their faces as they feel safe and cherished was incredible. Knowing we contributed to their happiness is deeply fulfilling and inspiring to others."</p>
